{"tid":491123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"甜美空姐教著救生衣 可愛動作令人由頭睇到尾","createTime":"2017-12-06T08:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T09:37:39.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00713f2c85b1d2b6248960ae599d85e4b15b13bc","tid":491123,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"飛機起飛前空中服務員都會向乘客示範如何使用機上求生設備，但好多乘客都好少理。不過，泰國微笑航空一位空姐做示範時，甜美可愛的動作令乘客由頭睇到尾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171205_PN_%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171205_PN_%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590-1.png&h=6df77e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171205_PN_%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171205_PN_%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590-1.png&h=6df77e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國知名訪談節目主持人木本植物在FB上分享了一段泰國微笑航空空姐為乘客演示安全須知的短片。他在文中寫到﹕「從清萊飛回來，忍不住想要分享，微笑泰航空姐超級可愛，認真地從到看到尾。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171205_PN_%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171205_PN_%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590-2.png&h=e3787984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171205_PN_%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90-3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171205_PN_%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590-3.png&h=2fd2791a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從短片可見一位樣子甜美的空姐示範穿救生衣時，一時張開手指示逃生位置，一時高舉安全卡紙，非常清純可愛。令人忍不住留心細看。短片曝光後瞬間被瘋傳，片中的空姐Nam一夜爆紅，成為不少男士的夢中情人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/12/20171205_PN_%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90-5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F12%2F20171205_PN_%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590-5.png&h=e9bd709d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2642583-甜美空姐教著救生衣-可愛動作令人由頭睇到尾\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2642583-%E7%94%9C%E7%BE%8E%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90%E6%95%99%E8%91%97%E6%95%91%E7%94%9F%E8%A1%A3-%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%B1%E9%A0%AD%E7%9D%87%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%BE&d=RrWYVrTiYs3SVwhRt8KSZKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fb443831\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2642583-甜美空姐教著救生衣-可愛動作令人由頭睇到尾</a>"},{"pid":"bbc73ebb7f5014f609669d2f4d7a862d8b3fcbf9","tid":491123,"uid":51978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"有鳩 不了"},{"pid":"35525df538215b5f7f34d43e9554675e777e640a","tid":491123,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有鳩 不了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bf4ffe4d6de2aaff3827aa513ece7005b9baf7","tid":491123,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9319847c37b7a20007cef1395958f63e76a958e5","tid":491123,"uid":25955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"男的也好"},{"pid":"192f106685254299cb7325a3c6e85953f9104d5e","tid":491123,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"You竟然......"},{"pid":"d7b785df9a4c2f98e7307993ea5837f3524f0eda","tid":491123,"uid":53026